{"tid":505293,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《溏心3》收視持續下跌，上周平均收視21.4點，下跌0.1點","createTime":"2017-12-21T03:23:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T04:09:37.000Z","uid":60281,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"02d9111665b18f72635bf491f95ceab42128f3b6","tid":505293,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T03:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無綫台慶劇《溏心風暴3》今晚播映18集，雖然劇集差唔多已經去到中段，不過收視依然冇起色，喺周二啱啱公佈跨平台收視，上周平均收視有21.4(約139萬觀眾收看)，比前一周跌咗0.1點，估唔到首周收視低開後，持續性下跌，唔知下一周嘅收視會唔會跌穿2字頭？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/realtime/article/20171221/57606184\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171221%2F57606184&d=Lae4Q969r7wfmezT87%2Byq2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=81028123\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171221%2F57606184&h=13c083c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/realtime/article/20171221/57606184</a>"},{"pid":"aa8a0a74bcbed64709b73ac63d29616dbc6807fe","tid":505293,"uid":51387,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:09:37.000Z","msg":"不過事實係香港唔收得, 但係大陸好受歡迎.<br />\n<br />\n頭先有個大陸同事啱啱同我講:<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">最近香港的电视剧---溏心风暴3很火哦，我都在追剧</span><br />\n<br />\n原文照copy &amp; paste, 唔好屌我打簡體同用匪語"}]}